metadata.name: ADONIS
metadata.description:
Adonis, brother of hybrid twins. Half-human and half-elf. The balance and peace of the world of elves and humans depend on the presence of these two. Each of these twins must be separated. And can only meet during the solar New Year when they change places.

Music: "Aref Niazi"
1500 x 2000 px , 11 sec
